0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:13:## 2. Decisões confirmadas\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:14:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:15:- Nome do produto: `shop-api`.\u001b[0m\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:16:- Aplicação exclusivamente SPA, sem páginas renderizadas no servidor.\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:17:- Stack aprovada: React, TypeScript, Vite, Tailwind CSS v4, Zod, Zustand, React \r\nRouter, TanStack Query, React Hook Form, Vitest, Testing Library, MSW e Playwright.\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:18:- O OpenAPI prevalece sobre a referência textual da API.\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:19:- Não existe carrinho anônimo no MVP. O usuário deve \u001b[7mautent\u001b[0micar-se \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mantes \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0madicionar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprimeiro \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mproduto.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:20:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mCadastro, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcheckout \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdetalhe \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpedido \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mfazem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mparte \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mMVP, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mmesmo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mtela \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcorrespondente \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mno \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprotótipo.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:21:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mFuncionalidades \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexibidas \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mno \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprotótipo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msuporte \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mno \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mOpenAPI \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mserão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mremovidas \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mMVP.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:22:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:23:## 3. Escopo do MVP\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:24:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:25:### 3.1 Incluído\u001b[0m\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:26:\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:27:- Navegação pública pelo catálogo, busca, categorias e detalhe do produto.\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:28:- Cadastro, login, persistência opcional da \u001b[7msessão\u001b[0m, expiração local e logout.\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:29:- Proteção de rotas e retorno à página de origem após \u001b[7mautent\u001b[0micação.\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:30:- Criação e manutenção de um carrinho \u001b[7mautent\u001b[0micado.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:31:- Checkout com endereço de entrega e forma de pagamento.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:32:- Criação de pedido e confirmação de sucesso.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:33:- Consulta paginada, filtro por período, detalhe e cancelamento de pedido.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:34:- Consulta, edição e cancelamento da conta do cliente.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:35:- Alteração de senha.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:36:- Estados de carregamento, vazio, erro, indisponibilidade e sucesso.\u001b[0m\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:50:- Especificações técnicas estruturadas além de `descricao` e `modelo`.\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:51:- Produtos recomendados ou relacionados.\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:52:- Múltiplos endereços salvos.\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:53:- Refresh token, login social ou \u001b[7mautent\u001b[0micação multifator.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:54:- Painel administrativo.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:55:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:56:Textos, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mlinks \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mindicadores \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdessas \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mfuncionalidades \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdevem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0maparecer \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcomo \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mações \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msimuladas \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mou \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mlinks \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdestino.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:57:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:58:## 4. Usuário e jornadas\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:59:\u001b[0m\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:60:### 4.1 Visitante\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:61:\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:62:Pode consultar categorias, buscar produtos, paginar resultados, abrir o detalhe \r\ne criar uma conta. Ao tentar adicionar um produto, deve ser encaminhado ao login, sem criar ou persistir itens \r\nlocalmente. Após \u001b[7mautent\u001b[0micar-se, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mretorna \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mà \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mrota \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0morigem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpode \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mrepetir \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0ma \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mação.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:63:\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:64:### 4.2 Cliente \u001b[7mautent\u001b[0micado\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:65:\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:66:Pode criar e gerenciar o carrinho, finalizar uma compra, consultar e cancelar \r\npedidos, alterar dados pessoais, trocar a senha, cancelar a conta e encerrar a \u001b[7msessão\u001b[0m.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:67:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:68:### 4.3 Jornadas principais\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:69:\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:70:1. Visitante navega no catálogo → abre produto → tenta adicionar → \u001b[7mautent\u001b[0mica-se \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m→ \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mretorna \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mao \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mproduto \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m→ \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0madiciona \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mao \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcarrinho.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:71:2. \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mVisitante \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcria \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconta \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m→ \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mrecebe \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconfirmação \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m→ \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mentra \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcom \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mas \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcredenciais \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcadastradas.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:72:3. \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mCliente \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0madiciona \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprodutos \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m→ \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mrevisa \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mquantidades \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m→ \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mabre \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcheckout \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m→ \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconfirma \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mendereço \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpagamento \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m→ \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcria \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpedido \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m→ \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvisualiza \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconfirmação.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:73:4. \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mCliente \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mabre \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpedidos \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m→ \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mfiltra \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpor \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mperíodo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m→ \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mabre \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdetalhe \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m→ \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcancela \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpedido \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mquando \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0ma \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mAPI \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0maceitar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0ma \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mtransição.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:74:5. Cliente abre a conta → edita dados ou senha → recebe confirmação.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:75:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:76:## 5. Mapa de rotas da SPA\u001b[0m\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:98:\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:99:- **RF-001:** O header deve exibir marca, busca, acesso ao carrinho e menu do \r\ncliente.\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:100:- **RF-002:** Em telas pequenas, a busca e a navegação por categoria devem \r\npermanecer acessíveis sem provocar overflow horizontal da página.\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:101:- **RF-003:** O menu do cliente deve refletir imediatamente o estado \r\n\u001b[7mautent\u001b[0micado \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mou \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdesautenticado.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:102:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-004:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mO \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mbadge \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcarrinho \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mrepresentar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0ma \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msoma \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdas \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mquantidades \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconfirmadas \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpelo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mbackend.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:103:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-005:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mO \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mfooter \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mmanter \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0ma \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcomposição \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvisual \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprotótipo, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mremovendo \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mlinks \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mfuncionalidade \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mno \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mMVP.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:104:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-006:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mToda \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnavegação \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mocorrer \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpelo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mReact \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mRouter, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mrecarga \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcompleta \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mda \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mSPA.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:105:\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:106:### 6.2 \u001b[7mAutent\u001b[0micação\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:107:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:108:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-010:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mO \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mlogin \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvalidar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me-mail \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msenha \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mantes \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mchamar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`POST \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m/api/v1/auth/login`.\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:109:- **RF-011:** A opção “manter conectado” deve persistir a \u001b[7msessão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mno \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`localStorage`; \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mela, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0ma \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msessão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0musar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`sessionStorage`.\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:110:- **RF-012:** A \u001b[7msessão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0marmazenar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mapenas \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mos \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcampos \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnecessários \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mlogin, \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mincluindo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mtoken, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexpiração, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcliente, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0musuário \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me-mail.\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:111:- **RF-013:** Token ausente ou expirado deve invalidar a \u001b[7msessão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mantes \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0muma \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mchamada \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprotegida.\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:112:- **RF-014:** Uma resposta `401` deve limpar a \u001b[7msessão\u001b[0m, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mlimpar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdados \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprivados \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mmemória \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mredirecionar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mao \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mlogin.\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:113:- **RF-015:** O logout deve chamar `POST /api/v1/auth/logout`; a \u001b[7msessão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mlocal \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mser \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mencerrada \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mmesmo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mse \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0ma \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mchamada \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mfalhar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpor \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mtoken \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexpirado \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mou \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mrevogado.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:114:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-016:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mA \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0minterface \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexibir \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m“Esqueci \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0ma \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msenha”, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpois \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexiste \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mendpoint \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcorrespondente.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:115:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:116:### 6.3 Cadastro\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:117:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:118:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-020:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mO \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcadastro \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msolicitar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mCPF, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnome, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnascimento, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me-mail, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msenha, \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mendereço \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0múnico \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcelular \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconforme \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`CreateClienteRequest`.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:119:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-021:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mMáscaras \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mCPF, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mCEP \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcelular \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdevem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mser \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mapenas \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mapresentação; \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mrequest \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0menviar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvalores \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnormalizados.\u001b[0m\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:120:- **RF-022:** O campo WhatsApp deve mapear para `celular.whatsApp`.\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:121:- **RF-023:** Após `201`, o usuário deve ser direcionado ao login com \r\nconfirmação de cadastro; o cadastro não \u001b[7mautent\u001b[0mica \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mautomaticamente.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:122:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-024:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mErros \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`409` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`422` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdevem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mser \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mapresentados \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mno \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mformulário \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msem \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mperder \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mos \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvalores \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpreenchidos, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexceto \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msenha \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mquando \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0ma \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpolítica \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msegurança \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexigir \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mlimpeza.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:123:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:124:### 6.4 Catálogo e categorias\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:125:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:126:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-030:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mA \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mhome \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mbuscar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcategorias \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprimeira \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpágina \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprodutos \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mem \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mparalelo.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:127:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-031:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mO \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcatálogo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0musar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`page`, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`size` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`searchword` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`GET \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m/api/v1/produto`.\u001b[0m\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:140:- **RF-043:** Produto indisponível deve exibir estado esgotado e CTA \r\ndesabilitado.\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:141:- **RF-044:** Avaliações, múltiplas imagens, descontos, entrega, \r\nespecificações inventadas e relacionados não devem ser renderizados.\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:142:\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:143:### 6.6 Regra de \u001b[7mautent\u001b[0micação ao adicionar\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:144:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:145:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-050:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mVisitante \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mque \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0macionar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m“Adicionar” \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mser \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mencaminhado \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpara \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`/entrar` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcom \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mretorno \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0minterno \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mà \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpágina \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0matual.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:146:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-051:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mNenhum \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mitem, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mquantidade, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpreço \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mou \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mintenção \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcompra \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mser \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpersistido \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mantes \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mlogin.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:147:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-052:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mApós \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mlogin, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0musuário \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mretorna \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mà \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0morigem; \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0ma \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0minclusão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msó \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mocorre \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mapós \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnova \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconfirmação \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexplícita \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mno \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mbotão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m“Adicionar”.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:148:\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:149:### 6.7 Carrinho \u001b[7mautent\u001b[0micado\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:150:\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:151:- **RF-060:** Na primeira inclusão sem `carrinhoId` persistido para o cliente \r\n\u001b[7mautent\u001b[0micado, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mfrontend \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mchamar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`POST \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m/api/v1/carrinho/criar` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mbody.\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:152:- **RF-061:** O `carrinhoId` retornado deve ser persistido de forma versionada \r\ne associado ao `clienteId` da \u001b[7msessão\u001b[0m.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:153:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-062:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mA \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0minclusão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mchamar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`POST \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m/api/v1/carrinho/items` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcom \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`produtoId`, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mquantidade \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpreço \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0matual \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mretornado \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpela \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mAPI \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprodutos.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:154:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-063:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mCarrinho \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconhecido \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mser \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcarregado \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpor \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`GET \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m/api/v1/carrinho/{carrinhoId}`.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:155:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-064:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mComo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mos \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mitens \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcontêm \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mtítulo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mfoto, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mos \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprodutos \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0múnicos \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdevem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mser \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mhidratados \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpor \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcache \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mou \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mchamadas \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdetalhe \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mparalelo.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:156:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-065:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mAlteração \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mquantidade \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mchamar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`PATCH \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m/api/v1/carrinho/items/{itemId}`.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:157:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-066:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mRemoção \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpedir \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconfirmação \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mchamar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`DELETE \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m/api/v1/carrinho/items/{itemId}`.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:158:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-067:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mFalha \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mmutação \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mrestaurar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0múltimo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mestado \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconfirmado \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mapresentar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0merro \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0macionável.\u001b[0m\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:161:\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:162:### 6.8 Checkout e criação do pedido\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:163:\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:164:- **RF-070:** O checkout deve exigir carrinho não vazio e \u001b[7msessão\u001b[0m válida.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:165:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-071:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mO \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mendereço \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mser \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0minicializado \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcom \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`GET \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m/api/v1/cliente/{clienteId}` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpermanecer \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0meditável \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mapenas \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpara \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpedido \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0matual.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:166:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-072:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mAs \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mformas \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpagamento \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpermitidas \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexatamente \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`Pix`, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`Cartao` \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`Boleto`.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:167:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-073:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mO \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mrequest \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`POST \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m/api/v1/pedido` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mseguir \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mOpenAPI \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconter \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mapenas \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`enderecoEntrega`, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`formaPagamento`, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`dataPedido` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`items`.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:168:- **RF-074:** O request não deve enviar `clienteId` nem `carrinhoId`.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:169:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-075:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`dataPedido` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mser \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mgerada \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mISO \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m8601 \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mno \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mmomento \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mda \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconfirmação.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:170:- **RF-076:** Durante o envio, o CTA deve impedir submissões duplicadas.\u001b[0m\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:173:\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:174:### 6.9 Pedidos\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:175:\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:176:- **RF-080:** A lista deve obter o CPF do perfil \u001b[7mautent\u001b[0micado \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mchamar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`GET \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m/api/v1/pedido` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcom \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mCPF, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mperíodo, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpágina \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mtamanho.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:177:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-081:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mFiltros \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msuportados \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mserão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdata \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0minicial \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdata \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mfinal; \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mchips \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mstatus \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprotótipo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mserão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0musados, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpois \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0ma \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mAPI \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0maceita \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mstatus \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcomo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mfiltro.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:178:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-082:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mStatus \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexibidos \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdevem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcorresponder \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexatamente \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0ma \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`Criado`, \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`EmProcessamento`, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`Processado`, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`Cancelado` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`Devolvido`, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcom \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mrótulos \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mamigáveis.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:179:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-083:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mO \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mtotal \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvisual \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mser \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcalculado \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpela \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msoma \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`quantidade \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m× \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvalorUnitario` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdos \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mitens \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mretornados.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:180:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-084:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mO \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdetalhe \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0musar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`GET \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m/api/v1/pedido/{pedidoId}` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexibir \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mendereço, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdata, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpagamento, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mstatus \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mitens.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:181:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-085:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mNomes \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mimagens \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mitens \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdevem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mser \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mhidratados \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mparalelo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpor \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mproduto, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcom \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mfallback \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcaso \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mproduto \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexista \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mmais.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:182:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-086:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mA \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mação \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcancelar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0menviar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexclusivamente \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`{ \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m\"status\": \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m\"Cancelado\" \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m}` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpara \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`PATCH \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m/api/v1/pedido/{pedidoId}`.\u001b[0m\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:184:\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:185:### 6.10 Conta do cliente\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:186:\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:187:- **RF-090:** A tela de dados deve carregar o cliente exclusivamente pelo \r\n`clienteId` da \u001b[7msessão\u001b[0m.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:188:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-091:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mA \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0matualização \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0menviar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mobjeto \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcompleto \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`UpdateClienteRequest` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpor \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`PUT`.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:189:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-092:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mCPF \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpermanecer \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvisível \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0meditável \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconforme \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcontrato, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcom \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0malerta \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconfirmação \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mantes \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0menviar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0muma \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0malteração.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:190:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-093:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mO \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mformulário \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mmanter \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mseparados \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mlogradouro, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnúmero \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcomplemento.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:191:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-094:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mA \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mtroca \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msenha \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0menviar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`senhaAtual` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`senhaNova` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mao \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mendpoint \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcorrespondente.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:192:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-095:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mA \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvalidação \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvisual \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msenha \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mseguirá \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprotótipo: \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mmínimo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0moito \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcaracteres, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0muma \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mmaiúscula, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mum \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnúmero \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mum \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcaractere \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mespecial \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mentre \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`!@#$%`.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:193:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RF-096:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mO \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcancelamento \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mda \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconta \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mficar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0márea \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mperigo, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexigir \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconfirmação \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexplícita \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mchamar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`DELETE \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m/api/v1/cliente/{clienteId}`.\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:194:- **RF-097:** Após cancelamento bem-sucedido, a \u001b[7msessão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mtodos \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mos \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdados \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprivados \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mlocais \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdevem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mser \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mremovidos.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:195:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:196:## 7. Contrato de integração\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:197:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:198:### 7.1 Regras gerais\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:199:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:200:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mA \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mURL \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mbase \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`VITE_API_BASE_URL`, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msem \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvalor \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprodução \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0membutido \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mno \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mbundle.\u001b[0m\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:205:- Erros seguem `ApiErrorResponse` e devem ser normalizados para um tipo único \r\nde erro da aplicação.\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:206:- O cliente não deve depender de texto exato de `message` para decidir regras.\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:207:- Requests protegidos usam `Authorization: Bearer <token>`.\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:208:- `401` invalida \u001b[7mautent\u001b[0micação; \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`404` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mapresenta \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mrecurso \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0minexistente; \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`409` \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mapresenta \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconflito; \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`422` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0massocia \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdetalhes \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mao \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mformulário \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mquando \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpossível; \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mfalhas \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`5xx` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mapresentam \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mrecuperação \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msem \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexpor \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdetalhes \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0minternos.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:209:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:210:### 7.2 Mapeamento de endpoints\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:211:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:212:| Feature | Método e endpoint | Acesso |\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:213:|---|---|---|\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:214:| Login | `POST /api/v1/auth/login` | Público |\u001b[0m\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:266:- **RNF-011:** Categorias e primeira página de produtos devem iniciar em \r\nparalelo.\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:267:- **RNF-012:** Hidratação de produtos do carrinho e pedidos deve usar \r\n`Promise.all`, deduplicação e cache por `produtoId`.\r\n  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:268:- **RNF-013:** Estado de servidor pertence ao TanStack Query; Zustand não deve \r\nduplicar listas ou respostas completas.\r\n> docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:269:- **RNF-014:** Persistência local deve ser mínima e versionada. Logout remove \r\n\u001b[7mautent\u001b[0micação \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcaches \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprivados, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mmas \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpode \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconservar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msomente \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvínculo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`clienteId` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m→ \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`carrinhoId`; \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcancelamento \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mda \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconta \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mremove \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mtambém \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0messe \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvínculo.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:270:- **RNF-015:** Nenhum HTML retornado pela API deve ser renderizado como markup.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:271:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RNF-016:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mO \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mfrontend \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mevitar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mlogs \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcom \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mtoken, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msenha, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mCPF, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mendereço \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mou \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdetalhes \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0merro \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msensíveis.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:272:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RNF-017:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mMutação \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcom \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvalor \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpreço \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0menviado \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpelo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcliente \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0musar \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mexclusivamente \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0múltimo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvalor \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mobtido \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mda \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mAPI; \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mfrontend \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconsidera \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mautoridade \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mfinal.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:273:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m**RNF-018:** \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mA \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0maplicação \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdeve \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0moferecer \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mretry \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mmanual \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpara \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconsultas \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnão \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mrepetir \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mautomaticamente \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mmutações \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0midempotentes.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:274:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-specification-v2.md:275:## 11. Critérios de aceite do MVP\u001b[0m\r\n### docs/frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md\r\n  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:67:| Rotas | React Router | URLs, proteção e lazy loading |\r\n  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:68:| Formulários | React Hook Form + Zod | Estado, validação e mensagens |\r\n  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:69:| Estado remoto | TanStack Query | Cache, deduplicação, invalidação e \r\nretries de leitura |\r\n> docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:70:| Estado local | Zustand | \u001b[7mSessão\u001b[0m mínima e metadados locais do carrinho |\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:71:| \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mTestes \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m| \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mVitest \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m+ \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mTesting \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mLibrary \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m+ \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mMSW \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m| \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mUnidade, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcomponentes \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mintegração \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m|\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:72:| E2E | Playwright | Jornadas críticas no navegador |\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:73:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:74:### 4.2 Propriedade do estado\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:75:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:76:| Estado | Dono | Persistência |\u001b[0m\r\n  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:77:|---|---|---|\r\n> docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:78:| Token e identidade mínima | Zustand `authStore` | `\u001b[7msession\u001b[0mStorage` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mou \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`localStorage` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m|\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:79:| `carrinhoId` por cliente | Zustand `cart\u001b[7mSession\u001b[0mStore` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m| \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`localStorage` \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mversionado \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m|\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:80:| Catálogo, categorias e detalhes | TanStack Query | Memória |\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:81:| Carrinho e pedidos | TanStack Query | Memória; servidor é autoridade |\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:82:| Busca, categoria, período e paginação | URL | Histórico do navegador |\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:83:| Campos de formulário | React Hook Form | Nenhuma |\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:84:| Menu, dialog e toast | Estado local/contexto leve | Nenhuma |\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:85:\u001b[0m\r\n  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:105:};\r\n  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:106:```\r\n  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:107:\r\n> docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:108:### 4.4 Estratégia de \u001b[7mautent\u001b[0micação\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:109:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:110:- O token é anexado somente às rotas protegidas.\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:111:- `\u001b[7mexpiraEm\u001b[0m` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mé \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mverificado \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mna \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0minicialização \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mantes \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mmutations \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprotegidas.\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:112:- A opção de permanência escolhe `localStorage` ou `\u001b[7msession\u001b[0mStorage`.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:113:- Não haverá refresh silencioso, pois a API não expõe refresh token.\u001b[0m\r\n> docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:114:- `401` encerra a \u001b[7msessão\u001b[0m e conserva apenas um `returnTo` interno.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:115:- Logout remoto é tentado antes da limpeza, sem impedir a limpeza local.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:116:- \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mMudança \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`clienteId` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mremove \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvínculo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mde \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcarrinho \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0musuário \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0manterior \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mda \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mmemória \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mativa.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:117:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:118:### 4.5 Estratégia de carrinho\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:119:\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:120:O OpenAPI não oferece “carrinho atual”. Portanto:\u001b[0m\r\n  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:121:\r\n> docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:122:1. O primeiro “Adicionar” \u001b[7mautent\u001b[0micado \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mprocura \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mum \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`carrinhoId` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mlocal \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0massociado \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mao \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`clienteId`.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:123:2. Sem ID, chama `POST /carrinho/criar` sem body e persiste o retorno.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:124:3. Adiciona o item com o último preço validado do produto.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0m  docs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:125:4. Com ID conhecido, `GET /carrinho/{id}` reidrata o carrinho.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:126:5. \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0m`404` \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mao \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mreidratar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mremove \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0msomente \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0maquele \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mID \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mlocal \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpermite \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcriar \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mum \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnovo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcarrinho \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mna \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpróxima \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0minclusão.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdocs\\frontend-implementation-plan-v2.md:127:6. \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mLogout \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnão \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mapaga \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mvínculo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpersistido \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mdo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpróprio \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcliente, \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpermitindo \u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[7m\u001b[0mretomada \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mapós \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mnovo \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mlogin; \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mcancelamento \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mda \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mconta \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0me \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[0mpedido \u001b[0m\u001b[7m\u001b[